pullrequest.title: Created OperationalSpaceController plugin example that uses DART

content.raw: For the record, this is not meant to be a final product by any stretch of the imagination; it's just a prototype, and there's a lot of cleanup that I intend to do. I'm creating the PR so everyone can see the concept in action before we take it too much further.
